# JACK Control API (optional)

Reference docs: [Control API](https://jackaudio.org/api/group__ControlAPI.html)

- Programmatic server control (start/stop/switch drivers) via `jack/control.h` types:
  - `jackctl_server_t`, `jackctl_driver_t`, `jackctl_parameter_t`
  - Create server: `jackctl_server_create`
  - Start/stop: `jackctl_server_open`/`jackctl_server_start`/`jackctl_server_stop`
  - Switch driver: `jackctl_server_switch_master`
- Signal helpers: `jackctl_setup_signals`, `jackctl_wait_signals`

Notes for this repo:
- We currently spawn `jackd` externally; Control API integration is a future enhancement when headers/libs are available across platforms.
